OL,3,CMan plays guitar during brain surgery
OL,4,Cto remove golf ball-sized tumour
OL,6,FAn amateur musician has spoken out
OL,7,Fabout what it was like to play the
OL,8,Fguitar during his 8-hour brain surgery.
OL,10,FColin Miller from Kent was diagnosed
OL,11,Fwith a life-limiting glioblastoma last
OL,12,Fyear after the left side of his face
OL,13,Fwent into spasm.
OL,15,FHe had an operation to remove a golf
OL,16,Fball-sized tumour in his brain at
OL,17,FKing's College Hospital in London.
