OL,3,CMan plays guitar during brain surgery
OL,4,Cto remove golf ball-sized tumour
OL,6,FDuring the procedure, he played the
OL,7,Finstrument so doctors could make sure
OL,8,Fhe wouldn't lose mobility in his hands
OL,9,Fand fingers.
OL,11,FColin says he was not nervous about
OL,12,Fthe procedure and "knew he'd be well".
OL,14,FHe said: "I was playing in my head a
OL,15,Fsong that was important to me. They
OL,16,Frepeatedly said 'play it again, play
OL,17,Fit again'.
OL,19,F"I'm a total geek so I was fascinated
OL,20,Fwith the technology around me.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
