OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F416A1732381959
OL,3,CMan plays guitar during brain surgery
OL,4,Cto remove golf ball-sized tumour
OL,6,F"I wasn't nervous. I had total faith
OL,7,Fwith the surgeons. I knew that I was
OL,8,Fgoing to be well. It's made me cherish
OL,9,Fevery day. This year, 2024, has been a
OL,10,Fbonus."
OL,12,FColin had chemotherapy and
OL,13,Fradiotherapy and is now monitored with
OL,14,Fthree-monthly scans.
OL,16,FJust over a year after the operation,
OL,17,FColin, from Herne Bay, is now taking
OL,18,Fon a month-long challenge to raise
OL,19,Fmoney for charity.
