OL,3,CMan plays guitar during brain surgery
OL,4,Cto remove golf ball-sized tumour
OL,6,FHe is walking 99 miles in November for
OL,7,Fcharity Brain Tumour Research, raising
OL,8,Fmore than #700 so far.
OL,10,FColin said: "I've always been keen on
OL,11,Fwalking and for this challenge I have
OL,12,Fa spreadsheet of all my walks so far,
OL,13,Fand I'm averaging six miles each day.
OL,15,F"I had to give up my driving licence,
OL,16,Fbut I can still move my body, and I
OL,17,Ffeel blessed to be able to do so in
OL,18,Fsupport of the brain tumour community."
