OL,6,FThere is more than 100 different types
OL,7,Fof brain tumours and the number of
OL,8,Fdiagnoses has risen by 11% in the last
OL,9,Fdecade, according to Brain Tumour
OL,10,FResearch.
OL,12,FThe disease is indiscriminate and can
OL,13,Faffect people at any age.
OL,15,FBrain Tumour Research spokesperson,
OL,16,FHugh Adams, said one in three people
OL,17,Fknow someone affected by a brain
OL,18,Ftumour.
