OL,6,FHe said: "It's a less common cancer
OL,7,Fbut it's not a rare form of cancer.
OL,8,FIt's uniquely devastating.
OL,10,F"The statistics around it are
OL,11,Fshocking. It's the biggest cancer
OL,12,Fkiller of children and adults under 40.
OL,14,F"If we're going to do something about
OL,15,Fit, we need to coalesce, amplify our
OL,16,Fvoice and make a difference."
